ios/build-device/
ios/DerivedData/
ios/*.xcodeproj/
ios/SourcePackages/
**/xcuserdata/
**/*.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/

# Business / strategy material — kept local, not part of the public showcase
*.docx
*.pdf
docs/INVESTOR_NARRATIVE.md

# iCloud / Finder duplicate artifacts (e.g. "BUILD_LOG 2.md", "Info 2.plist")
* [0-9].md
* [0-9].swift
* [0-9].plist
* [0-9].json

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
